dct_title_s: Tripoli 1:100,000. Tripoli. Sheet 1347. Series Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980
dct_description_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980. United States. Army Map Service. Relief shown by 25 metres and 5 metre (approximate) contour interval and spot heights. Copied from an Italian Map dated 1933. Revised to agree with a amap reproduced by 512(A.Fd.Svy) Coy. R.E. dated No. 1941. Reprint November 1942. Map is part of a set of 31 sheets.
